data.description: Don't wait to long to see this Key West style home located in Beach Haven a short walk across from the Beach. Enjoy the beautiful sunrises and long walks on the beach. Open floorplan with spacious kitchen overlooking Dining and Living Room. Kitchen offers gas stove top, double ovens, plenty of cabinets for storage and big island for entertaining. Master bedroom with walk in closet providing extra shelving & storage. Master bath has dual vanities, with separate shower and relaxing jetted tub.  3rd bedroom currently being used as an office now. Laundry room with washer, dryer and cabinetry. Enjoy the outdoors with open front porch and spacious screened in back porch for entertaining. Oversize 2 car garage with driveway parking. Home also features 2 extra parking spaces for your family and friends to visit. Community pool and lake.
